[[["nummod", "dep", "det", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound"], "Unit 5  A Recipe for a Delicious Friendship."], [["nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj"], "Everyone wants to have friends."], [["cc", "aux", "nsubj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "compound", "aux", "cop", "det", "acl", "mark", "dobj"], "But do you know that making friends can be a lot like making soup?"], [["discourse", "mwe", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod"], "That is, to enjoy a close friendship with another person, you have to act like a good chef."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "dobj", "det", "amod", "acl", "mark", "iobj", "dobj", "det", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj"], "First, you need a special recipe to tell you the things that you need."], [["advmod", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "advmod", "dobj", "advmod"], "Next, you have to prepare everything properly and then cook it carefully."], [["nsubj", "det", "compound", "cop", "det", "nmod", "case"], "All you need is a can of love,"], [["nmod", "case", "det", "acl", "case"], "Poured into a bowl of good"], [["nmod", "case", "amod"], "environment and similar interests,"], [["nummod", "nmod", "case", "compound"], "5 cups of time togetherX"], [["nummod", "nmod", "case"], "3 tons of encouragement,"], [["nsubjpass", "det", "acl:relcl", "nsubj", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "auxpass", "nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "amod"], "The poem you read on the left page was written by a fourteen-year old student."], [["nsubj", "cop", "case", "cc", "conj", "nsubjpass", "auxpass", "dobj", "compound"], "It is about friendship, and it is called Friendship Soup."], [["nsubj", "det", "ccomp", "mark", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "cop", "amod", "amod", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det"], "The poem shows that if you want to be someones good friend, you have to make an effort."], [["nsubj", "aux", "neg", "advmod", "advmod", "cc", "conj", "advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "mark"], "You cannot just sit back and wait for it to happen."], [["nmod", "case", "det", "amod", "nsubj", "xcomp", "mark", "dobj", "det", "acl", "mark", "iobj", "det", "dobj", "det", "amod"], "Like a good chef, you have to add some seasoning to make the soup a tasty dish."], [["nsubj", "det", "advmod", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "dobj", "amod", "amod"], "The poem also indicates that friendship requires many different ingredients."], [["nmod", "case", "nsubj", "cc", "conj", "amod", "cop", "advmod"], "For instance, trust and similar interests are very important."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "advmod", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nsubj", "aux", "nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "det", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "nmod", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "nmod", "case"], "If you really trust your friends, you can talk to them about any problem that you run into and share your feelings with them."], [["advcl", "mark", "nsubj", "cc", "conj", "nmod:poss", "dobj", "amod", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "amod", "xcomp", "dobj", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "cop", "dep", "nmod"], "If you and your friends have similar interests, you can spend more time doing things that you are both fond of."], [["nmod", "case", "nmod", "case", "compound", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "compound", "advmod", "mwe"], "In addition to trust and similar interests, friendship needs care as well."], [["nsubj", "advmod", "dobj", "advmod", "advcl", "advmod", "mark", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "nmod", "case", "det", "compound"], "You cant leave it alone, just as you cant leave soup on the stove unattended."], [["nsubj", "nmod", "case", "dobj", "nmod:poss", "cc", "conj", "advmod"], "Friendship, like soup, needs your time and attention, too."], [["advcl", "mark", "csubj", "dobj", "det", "xcomp", "nsubj", "nsubj", "advmod", "xcomp", "nsubj"], "Though having a friend keeps you busy, it also makes you happy."], [["nsubj", "det", "amod", "nmod", "case", "det", "nmod", "case", "amod", "aux", "advmod", "ccomp", "dobj", "nsubj", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "compound:prt"], "A good friend, like a bowl of good soup, can be just what you need when you feel down."], [["advmod", "advcl", "advmod", "nsubj", "advcl", "mark", "dobj", "amod", "cc", "conj", "dobj", "amod", "ccomp", "mark", "nsubj", "compound", "aux", "cop", "det", "acl", "mark", "ccomp", "nsubj", "aux", "dobj", "cc", "conj", "cc", "conj", "nsubj", "cop", "advmod", "case"], "Therefore, when it comes to keeping old friendships and starting new ones, remember that making friends can be a lot like making soupXit may take time and effort, but it is always worth it."], [["cc", "conj", "nmod", "case", "compound"], "XInterpreted and written by Theodore Pigott."], [["nsubjpass", "det", "auxpass", "nmod", "case", "compound"], "The poem is adapted from Friendship Soup."]]